Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ships from Le Garite and De Metrio are exchanging fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One of De Metrio's ships has lost control and is falling into our atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming down near this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.92,0:00:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A De Metrio ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.97,0:00:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was attacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ships that have lost their subspace fields can go ahead and break formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell them to avoid returning fire as much as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Any response from Le Garite?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We're trying all channels, but they continue to maintain silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this, Dizelmine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I even think of breaking my vow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and cease pursuit of my own path?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had already decided that day to defeat him, and return the Polyhedron to its rightful form.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will now fulfill my duty as king.
