Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm aboard Pharos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.25,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Effective immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.41,0:03:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,route all communications through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We received a communiqué
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,from De Metrio's trade representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Le Garite has commenced simultaneous attacks throughout the entire Polyhedron.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you trying to do, Dizelmine?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.29,0:04:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going in Orca, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to find out what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is something your brother started...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.20,0:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know that for sure, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.59,0:04:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to find out for sure, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.38,0:04:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Muginami...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, we'll just wing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan, it's too risky going alone, so I'll go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.88,0:05:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you two so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to head for Dizelmine's ship alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.94,0:05:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get wrinkles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the entire Polyhedron will become embroiled in conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to ask Dizelmine himself if that's his true intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.47,0:05:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With all due respect...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be in charge of the fleet until I return.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.85,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Villagiulio...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop giving me that look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,De Metrio Lu Villagiulio...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Arvirium!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.96,0:06:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A single Ovid has left the De Metrio flagship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Villagiulio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How predictable can that man get?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.77,0:06:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will deal with him myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.54,0:06:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a courtesy I extend as king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,King Dizelmine will be leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare Magoltul for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! Preparing Magoltul for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizelmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Some greeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.13,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply telling you wouldn't have convinced you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you two going to leave me behind like the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that wasn't our intention...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is between Le Garite and De Metrio...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where you're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Lan, you don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Muginami are my comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.93,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your problems are my problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're sad, I'm sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're happy, then I'm happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:07:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that make me sound creepy to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the three of us together vowed never to use our Vox for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're going to break that vow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,the three of us have to break it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.58,0:08:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Muginami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If the two of you were in trouble, I'd do the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you do the same, Lan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to fly, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.47,0:08:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Hiroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He insisted on coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.40,0:09:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I packed you lunches, in case you get hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I told him this wasn't a picnic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Uncle Hiroshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.59,0:09:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The three of you are the pretty faces that bring business to my shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.43,0:09:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go getting yourselves hurt, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come back safely, so I can see your happy faces again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.11,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Got that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.03,0:09:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be going, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Now go get 'em, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Orca, let's fly together once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.39,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Hupo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizelmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious about starting a war?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have I ever, even for a moment, stopped fighting to protect {\i1}the Polyhedron?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Villagiulio! We're sending support immediately!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.47,0:10:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We'll...what?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as he's saying that he's doing this for the sake of Polyhedron...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I must trust him, more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless of how badly I want to kill this bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Villagiulio...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Grania!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A ship is emerging from warp up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,More enemy ships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so shy right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit hiding and show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, I'm willing to listen to what you want to do with the Polyhedron, just like old times!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You owe me one.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.63,0:11:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That you, Izo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.95,0:11:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, who is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's some pretty sorry flying for the king of De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lax Lestorine Ha Kirius, here to assist in the name of honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who asked for your help?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't get the wrong idea.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.09,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only here to protect Kamogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kamogawa?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.93,0:11:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want this ocean to meet the same fate as De Metrio.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.06,0:12:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew a battle had begun
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.23,0:12:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,when we first came out of warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when Kirius said we were heading back to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He started threatening{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the captain of the spaceship to turn back.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't threaten him, I convinced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You "convinced" him by sticking a sword to his throat.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Relax.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't get in the way of any direct talks
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,between you two monarchs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't allow anyone to destroy Kamogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel the power of my swordsmanship
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,polished by the wild seas!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.06,0:12:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's your next move, Dizelmine?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just the two of us now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.86,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What do you say, let's be honest with each other?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Luckily, Moid's not here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Moid? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.71,0:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We have intel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he been telling you this time-?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.25,0:13:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you insinuating that he made me do this?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.12,0:13:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all my own decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Me! The King of Le Garite!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A mode change?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a Vox reading that's not in our database!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure it's not a sensor error?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.47,0:13:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm positive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.16,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying there's another Vox aside from Yurikano's Core?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you realize what you've done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really want to control this world so badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.64,0:14:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I listened to your plan to achieve peace through talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just once, but twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But to me, your vision of the future holds nothing but flaws,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and will end in failure.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's needed is power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You intend to create the world by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to listen to other opinions—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.63,0:14:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no need of other opinions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.60,0:14:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially not from the likes of you, who's only interested in personal gain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, nothing I say will convince you, when I look like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.68,0:15:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Laffinty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.81,0:15:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hold on, this is between me and...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is also our problem now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother, please stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Laffinty...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you to do things this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You love peace more than anyone.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}More than anyone,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you wished happiness for the people of Le Garite and the Polyhedron!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, life is a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act like you know me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You damn...idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy Vox has crash-landed on Maebara Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She went for an axe kick right off the bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a roundhouse kick to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,An {\i1}enzuigiri...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Vox particle readings are increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the nerve to attack your own sister?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd made up with Big Brother Giuvi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd vowed to work together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Lan's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizelmine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't the one who betrayed the other first...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.22,0:16:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizelmine...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.90,0:17:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He sided with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The people I despise more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The ones who tried to destroy the peace of the Polyhedron,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by defying me with force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a long time ago—!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you do it, Villagiulio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You, of all people, should have known!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The many sacrifices our ancestors had to make
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to build the peace and stability that we have today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That life is a miracle in itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dizelmine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.14,0:18:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me a damage report immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Madoka and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're checking on them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Circle of Rinne...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Feeding off a tainted heart..."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.93,0:19:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Big...Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Screw the Polyhedron.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, all I care about is killing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Big...Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Big Brother!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Research institutes around the world are reporting changes in quantum particle levels!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's starting to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing that happened 20,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.50,0:20:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues, Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the entire universe will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.05,0:20:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.69,0:20:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you plan on doing anything more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We will not forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.36,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.62,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Lan! Muginami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon has risen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.18,0:21:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka! Lan?!
