Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.60,0:23:11.66,ED2rom2-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur1.8}itsumo koko de matteru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:11.66,ED2eng2-1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur1}for me to wait in
Dialogue: 1,0:23:01.60,0:23:11.66,ED2eng2-2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,250)\blur1.8}for me to wait in
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.99,0:23:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, we're in trouble, and I mean big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.14,0:23:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be the nether world?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.33,0:23:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we die?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka, could it be that we're inside the Rinne?
